{"tid":1157110,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有有人好心痛香港搞成咁","createTime":"2019-05-16T04:48:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-16T08:04:42.000Z","uid":145589,"like":46,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e7ef2a2d4ca221a53958aea0cca6070756d71ed7","tid":1157110,"uid":145589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T04:48:09.000Z","msg":"逃犯條例、海外醫生<br />\n基本上法治同醫療都不停被侵蝕緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前香港無論係雨革、旺角魚旦<br />\n一仗一仗都輸緊<br />\n有能力對抗中共嘅人基本上都移民<br />\n好無力但好唔甘心<br />\n要等到七一先有遊行<br />\n到時上咗街其實都冇咩搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"242a8a309eb9bd0d787d1ef3d712187eea87b1d9","tid":1157110,"uid":62837,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T04:54:06.000Z","msg":"下 香港抵死架wo<br />\n你問下d老野97個陣做緊咩野 有幾多出黎反過<br />\nd泛民仲仆街 成撚日就係想將民主交俾下一代<br />\n自己就拍攞友訓棺材"},{"pid":"5592da2ed2a947257ba7677a777dc0313cf4f4f6","tid":1157110,"uid":145589,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"242a8a309eb9bd0d787d1ef3d712187eea87b1d9","tid":1157110,"uid":62837,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T04:54:06.000Z","msg":"下 香港抵死架wo<br />\n你問下d老野97個陣做緊咩野 有幾多出黎反過<br />\nd泛民仲仆街 成撚日就係想將民主交俾下一代<br />\n自己就拍攞友訓棺材"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T04:59:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我就係身受其害"},{"pid":"bdd01852dd8ddf219ecbf7a988bd67ca032e5255","tid":1157110,"uid":67315,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T05:04:10.000Z","msg":"點解要等七一先去遊行"},{"pid":"a641195202679ce0cf8c333c8ff7804c34707697","tid":1157110,"uid":145589,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bdd01852dd8ddf219ecbf7a988bd67ca032e5255","tid":1157110,"uid":67315,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T05:04:10.000Z","msg":"點解要等七一先去遊行"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T05:08:02.000Z","msg":"因為最大型<br />\n有小型遊行都會去嘅"},{"pid":"c68c889f0e2c0cff8e1c9a0f37df8ebaaab9eec